['<p>','The right decision for everyone is to be cleansed from every sin.','Uamuzi nzuri kwa mut yote ni kwa mwenye kutakaswa kwa kila dhambi ','</p>'],
['<p>','God destroyed four cities with fire for Homosexuality. (Gen. 19:1-17; 23-28) Even as Sodom and Gomorrah&#44; and the cities about them in like manner&#44; giving themselves over to fornication&#44; and going after strange flesh&#44; are set forth for an example&#44; suffering the vengeance of eternal fire. (Jude 7)','Mungu aliharibu miji ine kwa mot kwa ajili ya ufisadi muu (Mwanzo 19:1-17; 23-28) Kama vile sodoma na Gomora&#44; na miji iliyo kuwa kandokando waliofuata uasherati kwa jinsi moja ja hawa&#44; wakaenda kufuata mambo ya mwili yasiyo ya asili&#44; imewekwa kuwa dalili&#44; wakiadhibiwa katika moto ya milele (Yuda 1:7)','</p>'],
